# Zoho SMTP credentials — powers the landing-page inquiry form (app/api/inquire).
# SMTP_USER: a Zoho mailbox login for aeterna-ehr.com (e.g. inquire@aeterna-ehr.com
#            or clint.mariano@aeterna-ehr.com).
# SMTP_PASS: a Zoho APP-SPECIFIC password — generate at
#            accounts.zoho.com -> Security -> App Passwords. NOT your login password.
# Set these in Vercel -> Project -> Settings -> Environment Variables.
SMTP_USER=
SMTP_PASS=

# Optional overrides (defaults shown):
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.zoho.com
# SMTP_PORT=465
